{"tid":2081218,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook讓步 將屏蔽特朗普等仇恨言論","createTime":"2020-06-27T05:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T09:49:42.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"23d3e977cc8ae6dd65e47ba0f78169de4438c417","tid":2081218,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"Facebook周五股價急挫8%，主因公司面對有史以來的最大型廣告商杯葛行動。公司創辦人兼行政總裁朱克伯格周五宣布，將會修改公司政策，屏蔽及刪除涉及種族歧視等仇恨言論、或影響2020年美國大選的誤導訊息，政治人物亦不會獲得豁免。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2680000/2681168/673526_01_02_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2680000%2F2681168%2F673526_01_02_1024_1024.jpg&h=3114c763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然朱克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）沒有直接點名美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump），但外間相信今次行動，一大目標是特朗普近期一連串被指煽動暴力的帖文。<br />\n<br />\nNAACP and the Anti-Defamation League等美國人權組織，6月17日發起Stop Hate For Profit行動，呼籲企業對漠視仇恨言論的廣告平台說不，矛頭正是Facebook。<br />\n<br />\n他們表示，杯葛行動將直至Facebook就平台上的失實資訊及仇恨言論，作出「具意義行動」（meaningful action）為止。<br />\n<br />\n美國電訊業龍頭Verizon、戶外服飾企業North Face及Patagonia、可口可樂及聯合利華等巨企，近日先後宣布停止於Facebook，以至所有社交平台刊登廣告。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook去年廣告收入高達697億美元，為僅次於Google的數碼推廣平台，也是公司最重要的收入來源，比重高達99%。<br />\n<br />\nRead More:<br />\nFacebook股價遭拖累 朱克伯格表態：社交媒體非仲裁者@hket.com<br />\n抗議不審特朗普帖文 Facebook員工罷工@hket.com"},{"pid":"b91c2bd7f544d13b8ebfb6667f5d2bf3999887e3","tid":2081218,"uid":73143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:12:59.000Z","msg":"左膠死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbd2b5f1c757ebf74c44b8ef2275801a379bdbb","tid":2081218,"uid":106001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b91c2bd7f544d13b8ebfb6667f5d2bf3999887e3","tid":2081218,"ui